OL,6,F"Significant internal failings" were
OL,7,Fidentified within the review and were
OL,8,Freflected in its ability to identify
OL,9,Fpoor performance at hospitals, care
OL,10,Fhomes and GP surgeries.
OL,12,FStreeting said he was "stunned by the
OL,13,Fextent of the failings" revealed in
OL,14,Fthe report.
