OL,4,Cas report outlines 'failings'
OL,6,FDr Jack and Sarah Hawkin's daughter,
OL,7,FHarriet, was stillborn after mistakes
OL,8,Fwere made by maternity staff in
OL,9,FNottingham. They say the CQC watchdog
OL,10,Ffailed them in its handling of their
OL,11,Fcase.
OL,13,FSpeaking to ITV News, Dr Hawkins said:
OL,14,F"I'm not sure how they have been
OL,15,Fallowed and how they have seen fit to
OL,16,Foperate as they're doing.
OL,18,F"I think that we need to have a public
OL,19,Finquiry into how there are so many
OL,20,Fmaternity scandals in full view of the
OL,21,Fregulator."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
