OL,6,FDr Jack Hawkins said the CQC is not
OL,7,Ffit for purpose and that it has 'let
OL,8,Fus down personally'
OL,10,FOf the locations the CQC has the power
OL,11,Fto inspect, it is estimated about one
OL,12,Fin five health organisations have
OL,13,Fnever been inspected.
OL,15,FIt was also found that there was a
OL,16,Flack of experience among some staff,
OL,17,Fincluding examples of inspectors
OL,18,Fvisiting hospitals.
