OL,6,FSome had said they had never been in a
OL,7,Fhospital prior to conducting an
OL,8,Fassessment and one inspector of a care
OL,9,Fhome stated they had never met someone
OL,10,Fwith dementia.
OL,12,FThe report found inspection numbers
OL,13,Fwere still well below pre-Covid level.
OL,15,FIt also found a lack of consistency in
OL,16,Fthe watchdog's assessments and issues
OL,17,Fwith its IT system.
