OL,6,FMr Streeting said: "When I joined the
OL,7,Fdepartment, it was already clear that
OL,8,Fthe NHS was broken and the social care
OL,9,Fsystem in crisis.
OL,11,F"But I have been stunned by the extent
OL,12,Fof the failings of the institution
OL,13,Fthat is supposed to identify and act
OL,14,Fon failings. It's clear to me the CQC
OL,15,Fis not fit for purpose.
