OL,6,F"We cannot wait to act on these
OL,7,Ffindings, so I have ordered the
OL,8,Fpublication of this interim report so
OL,9,Faction can begin immediately to
OL,10,Fimprove regulation and ensure
OL,11,Ftransparency for patients.
OL,13,F"I know this will be a worrying
OL,14,Fdevelopment for patients and families
OL,15,Fwho rely on CQC assessments when
OL,16,Fmaking choices about their care.
