OL,6,FKate Terroni, CQC's interim chief
OL,7,Fexecutive, said: "We accept in full
OL,8,Fthe findings and recommendations in
OL,9,Fthis interim review, which identifies
OL,10,Fclear areas where improvement is
OL,11,Furgently needed."
OL,13,FShe added: "Many of these align with
OL,14,Fareas we have prioritised as part of
OL,15,Four work to restore trust with the
OL,16,Fpublic and providers by listening
OL,17,Fbetter, working together more
OL,18,Fcollaboratively and being honest about
OL,19,Fwhat we've got wrong.
